track.name: Alberta
comments: Oh no! Every time I hear this track, I spend the rest of the day singing, "Alberta, Alberta!"  I don't mind but humanity does.
The melody is very reminiscent of a Big Joe Turner tune called Corinna, Corinna but in a slower pace.  Clapton is to be honored for bringing American Blues back to America.  Along with Bonnie Raitt.
